697
00:35:51,510 --> 00:35:53,270
As long as you keep it secret,

698
00:35:53,270 --> 00:35:55,030
they’ll be safe.

699
00:35:56,310 --> 00:35:58,360
Yes. I understand.

700
00:36:23,060 --> 00:36:25,160
Your Highness, yesterday my father said

701
00:36:25,800 --> 00:36:27,710
