702
00:36:28,110 --> 00:36:29,790
with obvious bruises on her forehead?

703
00:36:29,790 --> 00:36:30,600
Yes.

704
00:36:31,040 --> 00:36:31,640
But Your Highness,

705
00:36:32,390 --> 00:36:33,070
